Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.25,0:00:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險呀！阿秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心吧，不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這短劍好漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是阿，我在父王的房間找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.25,0:00:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟發生什麼事啊，藍迪斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:01:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種情況我不用多講了吧，陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道在跟誰說話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然你曾經對我有恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已不再是你的待衛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在的勢力和你是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜，你將來就做我的奴隸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不做你的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要做公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但爸爸說要把重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變成自己的奴隸的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要，我一定要做公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能失去我的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王子，你死期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些東西不能摘來吃的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是呀，與阿秀無關的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我叫他爬上去摘的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們像很生氣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.93,0:02:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫我走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們只是摘了些水果
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莫非也要斬頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我取你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀！快走啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走啊！阿秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒事，做了個惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要換衣服，你先出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主，我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我靜一靜呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Presented by Woodpecker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼時候了？蒂雅娜還未起床？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是呀，她在更衣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎？叫她好好裝扮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若她能和迪拉姆王子一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我和咕普達的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就會更加密切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出賣自己女兒的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來維持自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太過份了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這怎算得是出賣自己女兒幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼說，迪拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是現在最強盛國家的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本就是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別再囉囉唆唆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再多管閒事，我把你也賣掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快去給我叫蒂雅娜出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到你連自己的女兒也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下來這一位靚女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保証令你們垂涎欲滴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,張開雙眼，不要眨眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,日間可叫她做任何工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一到了晚上，她比你勁得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣，年青人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那麼年輕不會想買女僕的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實買回去也不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.53,0:08:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是我從哈拉度買回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很不錯的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啦，就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出六十拉素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出八十
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有出高過這個價的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出八十五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出八十五呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出一百
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一百
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有出多過一百的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有高過一百的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個美人兒就屬於這位先生了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，下來一個更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未買的，千萬不要走寶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好正呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別害羞，讓人家看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么可爱的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是機會難逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的鼻子長得多漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮膚又白又滑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那櫻桃小咀很誘人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這女孩子底價四十拉索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五十
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出六十
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出七十！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，就七十賣給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看看她多辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對女孩子別那麼粗暴好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事呀，年青人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也想買嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是絕對不會買女孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不買的話就別攪攪震
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來告訴你，小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我這生意是皇室御準的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,警告你，別多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別碰我呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看不出這小子也頗厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,豈有此理，好好的教訓他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一點三腳貓功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能打贏我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小子，你身手不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,借你的馬兒一用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這馬是我的，快還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快下來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別走啊！打劫呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我們現在已脫險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但待會太陽下山就會有野獸出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，要你為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看不過眼才這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的，你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜，像個女孩子的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用那麼害怕呀，都市人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些魚兒的名字叫「水妖」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實它們是食肉獸來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們剛才也見到它們多兇殘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下子就把馬兒吃過清光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千萬不要接近它們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如我來教你這兒生存的秘訣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就用這女孩子作報酬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這提意不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,年青人，你想殺了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,枉我剛才還救你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這樣簡直是恩將仇報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,醒目的就把那女孩子交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你休想，沒那麼容易
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以為可以走得那麼容易？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想到那兒去呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還走…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,截住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看你們能跑到那兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡！我跟你拼過！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走吧，菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別跟小孩子浪費時間玩耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留下他們，只會阻手阻腳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基恩內，你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的被她嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來她是個女孩子來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開我呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放手呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一次過捉了兩個美人兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這叫一箭雙鵰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是不是可把她們據為己有？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先讓大王過目然後再作決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的感到很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜忽然生病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以沒出來迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是因為知道王子到訪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一時緊張過度所以生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我想她很快就會復原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天要王子你白走一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王別這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾你們真的不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我那麼榮幸得到你的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那該是我迪拉姆的光榮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次除了要多謝我父王之外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就一定要多謝藍迪斯王你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對我所做的一切安排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我今次拜訪你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒機會和美麗的公主見面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算我和他沒緣份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心吧，我保証再過兩三個月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王子一定能見到她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然今天令你好失望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我已另為你準備了美女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了，迪拉姆王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想知道你們咕普達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會怎樣處置那班遊牧民族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然大王那麼想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就不妨跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要把這個民族殺個片甲不留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你們可有聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傳說中的勇者，這回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傳說中的勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像風一般無影無蹤的勇者？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是那一班遊牧民族的信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那千千萬萬的遊牧民族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會效力於一個傳說中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我最近聽聞這傳說中的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,準備推翻王室制度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,建立市民國家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真有這回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到你也會相信這種謠傳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們還未找到蒂雅娜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們已經確定公主離開了皇宮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但曾見過公主的人不太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以這次要把公主尋回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不定，她已離開了多利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是真的這樣，就真的令人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的探子今晨回報消息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在多利亞城外有遊牧民族出現
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你終於都睡醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎你到遊牧民族的馬車上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們快點放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也很兇呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以為自己是誰呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是多利亞公主，蒂雅娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽到了沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她說自己是公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主也會穿成男孩子那樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣撒謊，我真的服了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你現在才害羞也太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你昏迷不醒時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒穿衣服的樣子已被人看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以，你是不是真的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我們和你一樣都是女僕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且還是新來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你一起的那個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的身份亦是一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜，菲娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菲娜，你姊姊在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我停手好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀！不要停呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求你不要停手呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳們想怎樣對菲娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們在教她怎去做女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她學懂了怎去服待主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不會成為水妖的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看，菲娜也差不多學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要看清楚一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為下一個就輪到你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們教你，你要好好學習呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不看！我不看呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若你覺得那麼討厭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們可以立即把菲娜逐出營外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為何要這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在你未被決定歸那個主人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就要乖乖的聽我命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽清楚了沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你們不要對菲娜亂來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看你這位公主也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們開始了，好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要記住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人問你，你一定要答應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你覺得怎樣？有感覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真是個沒用的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說自己是公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你現在應知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向我們撒謊，會有什麼後果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮膚真滑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:12.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是很刺激呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道怎回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒可能不知道的，到底怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的身體已經告訴了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想盡快有你自己的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有這樣說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,羞死人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來要我出馬才行，是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實她的反應也不俗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們會對蒂雅娜女僕好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你快說：求求你吧，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求你令我舒服點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那怎麼行？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人叫你說就說吧，別再死忍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.43,0:22:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想蒂雅娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是生病而是下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.07,0:22:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說得對不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身為國王也管不了自己的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過，他送給我的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.43,0:22:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也算得是一流貨色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在公主未回來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就要好好的服待我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.11,0:23:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞王國
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藍迪斯國王的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還要撒謊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這女孩真是頗厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.39,0:23:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一面反坑，一面在享受
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們再多等一會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她就能成為我們的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.11,0:24:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時我一定會令你欲仙欲死
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.03,0:24:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們看看她的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.31,0:24:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已興奮到不能說話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.11,0:24:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，時候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快給她把頸環戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.23,0:24:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀！絕對不要，不要呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.75,0:24:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖地給我收聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.67,0:24:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，有誰想在頸環上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.07,0:24:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刻上自己名字的話就站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.55,0:24:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.27,0:24:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼漂亮的女孩人人都想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王，照老規矩由你決定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.05,0:24:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.09,0:24:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都有分享的權利呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:25:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？連大王你都想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.33,0:25:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那當然啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.29,0:25:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們說我身邊的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.13,0:25:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底有誰能跟她比
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王，你次次都是這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.09,0:25:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧，順次序
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.09,0:25:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.33,0:25:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，我想在此逗留一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.05,0:25:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.13,0:25:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,觀迎你到我們的營地區來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不過跟你玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.69,0:25:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想跟你們作無謂的比試
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.49,0:25:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？那麼大口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.29,0:25:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是男子漢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就拔劍和我比試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.09,0:25:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然是這樣，點到即止？好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.65,0:25:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.05,0:25:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.57,0:26:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這衰人呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.41,0:26:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想你們都是不會讓我留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.53,0:26:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這位兄弟可以跟我們比試一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.33,0:26:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.69,0:26:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我收聲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.29,0:26:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.13,0:27:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他很厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.41,0:27:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為何不殺了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.09,0:27:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為你根本罪不至死！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.45,0:27:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果要向我的侮辱賠罪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.01,0:27:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人的命已足夠有餘了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.13,0:27:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧，我現在向你賠罪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.05,0:27:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以把劍收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.25,0:27:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫做迪歐
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是這個部族的大王，那你呢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.38,0:28:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.14,0:28:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫做阿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.78,0:28:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.54,0:28:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王請原諒我戴著這面具
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.94,0:28:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不用介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.34,0:28:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是我們遊牧民族表示
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.66,0:28:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傳達風之友情的誓言方式
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.06,0:28:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是代表我們永遠的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.02,0:28:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.06,0:28:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那女孩子我決定送給阿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.94,0:28:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家可有意見？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.90,0:28:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喜歡這份禮物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.58,0:28:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在四處流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.18,0:28:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒時間來照顧其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.34,0:28:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這女孩子自稱多利亞公主
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.94,0:28:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不想試一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.54,0:28:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用考慮了！你收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.42,0:29:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧！各位
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.94,0:29:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在就為阿秀殿下慶祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.90,0:29:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.26,0:29:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.18,0:29:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜，你好漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.62,0:29:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要緊記，要開心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.86,0:29:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然人家不要你就弊傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.18,0:29:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是阿秀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.94,0:29:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若你真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.14,0:29:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我心裡日思夜想的阿秀，那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.50,0:30:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是屬於你的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.62,0:30:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不用我來服待你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.02,0:30:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是不是覺得我很醜呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.22,0:30:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是，你很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.18,0:30:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.58,0:30:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以在你面前做這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.02,0:30:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夠啦！阿蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.18,0:30:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來你真的是阿秀…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.98,0:31:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.34,0:31:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你，接受我做你的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.22,0:31:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你一生一世的來享用我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.54,0:31:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會盡心盡力的來服待你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.98,0:31:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不論任何艱難的事我也肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.42,0:31:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人呀，你愛我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.34,0:31:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別再說了，蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.38,0:31:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.42,0:31:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經不再是什麼蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.14,0:31:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若果我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.90,0:31:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你所說的那個多利亞國
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.42,0:31:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藍迪斯王的公主蒂雅娜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.30,0:31:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算拼了我這條命
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.30,0:31:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在都要親手殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.54,0:31:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不可以這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不依呀！我要做公主
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.98,0:31:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會做僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.14,0:31:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要做公主
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.10,0:31:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要做公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.42,0:31:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…我不要做蒂雅娜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.98,0:31:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要做僕人！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.30,0:31:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的決定了這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.82,0:31:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.52,0:31:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.94,0:32:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的很多謝你，我的主人！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.06,0:32:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一生一世我都會服待你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.42,0:32:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到我生命完結為止
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.98,0:32:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那以後我就叫你從前的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.94,0:32:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫阿蒂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的，我很喜歡這名字
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.94,0:32:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.98,0:32:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀，我最愛的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.94,0:33:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.94,0:33:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,醜死人呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.38,0:33:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了！你很喜歡是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.94,0:33:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.46,0:33:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.02,0:33:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣了？阿蒂，這樣好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.14,0:33:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.42,0:33:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請主人你幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.14,0:33:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.58,0:33:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好舒服呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.02,0:33:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿蒂是屬於主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.46,0:34:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你好好的享用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.98,0:34:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人，我應該怎樣做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.46,0:34:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿蒂，別那麼緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.22,0:34:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你放鬆點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.26,0:34:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不想的話就不要做
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.94,0:34:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要呀！主人！求求你繼續呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.66,0:34:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.06,0:34:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我受不了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.42,0:35:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人，早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.86,0:35:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.98,0:35:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人起床了我也還未起床
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.54,0:35:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.98,0:35:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.22,0:35:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只許今次，下不為例
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.66,0:35:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.86,0:35:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了，主人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.34,0:35:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.26,0:35:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去食早餐吧，我們要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.42,0:35:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.46,0:35:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.02,0:35:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，我們來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.10,0:35:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.26,0:36:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們快過來吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.98,0:36:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,經過那漫長的一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.26,0:36:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你們今天一定很餓的了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.02,0:36:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的很厲害呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.12,0:36:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一晚就令這丫頭貼貼服服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.98,0:36:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.34,0:36:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惡馬要被惡人騎的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.58,0:36:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們說是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.18,0:36:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.34,0:36:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.22,0:36:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是不是很想跟住阿秀殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.42,0:36:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.66,0:36:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來我除了劍術之外
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.42,0:36:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連馴奴術也不及阿秀殿下你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.90,0:36:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別這樣說，你太厚待我了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.98,0:36:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尤其是這個那麼好的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.94,0:36:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們好恩愛呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.98,0:36:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相處一晚就那麼好真難得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.06,0:36:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的，丫頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.50,0:36:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你現在叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.94,0:36:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿蒂，我現在的名字叫阿蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.66,0:37:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿蒂，名字很好聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.22,0:37:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨晚有好好服待殿下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.10,0:37:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有啊，還很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.94,0:37:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王子，你死期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.26,0:37:29.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我取你的命！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.22,0:37:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.99,0:37:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀，快走呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.07,0:38:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯，我在父王的房間裡找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.11,0:38:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蒂雅娜，你將來做我的僕人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.55,0:38:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.51,0:38:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要做你的僕人！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.95,0:38:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要做公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.31,0:38:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是爸爸說要將重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.63,0:38:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要變成僕人才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.31,0:38:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不依啊！我一定要做公主
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.19,0:39:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.63,0:39:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們想到那兒去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.63,0:39:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞國的阿秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.55,0:39:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.31,0:39:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別像昨天那麼兇好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.59,0:39:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多利亞國的阿秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.43,0:39:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有蒂雅娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.35,0:39:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎會知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.11,0:39:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是不會忘記那家紋的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.27,0:39:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本就不用去隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.89,0:39:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這已是個公開的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.19,0:39:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果阿秀想找多利亞王
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.67,0:39:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亦即是你爸爸來報仇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.59,0:39:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他昨晚和你一起時
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.51,0:39:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就已經可以落手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.89,0:39:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你昨晚偷聽我們兩人說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.09,0:39:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.97,0:39:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是聽到你們說話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.33,0:39:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那是無意中聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.85,0:39:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是存心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.57,0:39:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那為何…？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.89,0:39:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我聽到叫床聲
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.09,0:39:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就不知不覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.89,0:39:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起，是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.53,0:40:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你為了什麼要專程來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.29,0:40:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了和巴善陛下的盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你認識我爸爸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.17,0:40:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以收下這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.89,0:40:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是？…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.89,0:40:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其餘的遺族現在四處奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.81,0:40:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,散居的遊牧民族
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.89,0:40:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分成十二支族
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.57,0:40:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它就是統御的信物！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.97,0:40:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.01,0:40:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.97,0:41:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已經變成了不起的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.89,0:41:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿秀殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.01,0:41:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以收下它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.81,0:41:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.33,0:41:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會好好珍惜它！但…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.89,0:41:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.97,0:41:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是被風所培育出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.01,0:41:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,風之國的王位
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.53,0:41:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要由來自風的民族來承繼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.49,0:41:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當我願望達成之時
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.93,0:41:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會把這王位和家紋歸還
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.81,0:41:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有意見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.37,0:41:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那在你擁有的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.13,0:41:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這十二支部族的十萬戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.05,0:41:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由今天開始，就以命相陪